column1:
```csharp
// Serialize an object to an XML string
public static string SerializeObjectToString(this T toSerialize)
{
    XmlSerializer xmlSerializer = new XmlSerializer(toSerialize.GetType());
    using (StringWriter textWriter = new StringWriter())
    {
        xmlSerializer.Serialize(textWriter, toSerialize);
        return textWriter.ToString();
    }
}
```
,"使用 `StringWriter` 而不是 `StreamWriter`:

```javascript
function myFunction(number) {
    var x = number;
    // ... more initializations
    // here need to wait until flag == true

    function waitForFlag() {
        if (flag) {
            // ... do something
        } else {
            setTimeout(waitForFlag, 10); // Check again after 10ms (or adjust as needed)
        }
    }

    waitForFlag();
    // ... the rest of the function will be handled inside waitForFlag when flag is true
}
```
,"因为浏览器中的 JavaScript 是单线程的（除了 Web Workers，但这里没有涉及），并且一段 JavaScript 代码必须执行完毕才能执行另一段代码，所以你的语句：

```#!/bin/bash
f() {
  # echo function name, "f" in this case
  echo ${FUNCNAME[0]}
}

f # Call the function to test

printf "Usage: %s: blah blah blah \n" $(basename $0) >&2;
```
